{"id": "33546309e42b7009ef0eba0f027cfe32ffad09c0666e623db566eac91c0c72c4", "item_id": "86273c707e:0", "text": "Tractor distributes tasks to a farm of execution servers. It manages large queues of concurrent jobs from many users, enforcing dependencies and scheduling policies"}
{"id": "be395e4777a5b8f9da43374cf2ccdbec0c80a171abfe12bdd3128860f7b0d591", "item_id": "86273c707e:1", "text": "You can access the Tractor Spool panel in Solaris by clicking on the + icon in any UI pane."}
{"id": "e9180c0567de06b4169031913db638a4b7431bc542c9ce5d9272fc775c89ce94", "item_id": "86273c707e:2", "text": "Spool to"}
{"id": "984cfe27b73d034410351f34b421cb1c326eb5d957a330a7954fdb224863fe9b", "item_id": "86273c707e:3", "text": "Whether to spool to LocalQueue or a Tractor farm"}
{"id": "eb463ce8f83db65d128198893fd97663f8bc7e65e8beca642c2db8112efe1b45", "item_id": "86273c707e:4", "text": "Render Node"}
{"id": "a8f1863e201e29f26c8f2921f3127282999b4f01ac83d599362a62856769bb60", "item_id": "86273c707e:5", "text": "Choose which USD Render ROP node you wish to spool"}
{"id": "1a4ebec9c1477af65c1427ddf9f6ab60433fb1a922c9000412b2b6e6f52c3166", "item_id": "86273c707e:6", "text": "Render Threads"}
{"id": "8b2cc703ffe26cb53a8c1de0f842152dde02c819b06e0a3857093af8bb7c738f", "item_id": "86273c707e:7", "text": "The number of threads to use for rendering.  0 means to use all available threads."}
{"id": "b6416e2ac7740df2b1ed8c610d7a9cfa48740008c5fe557cb51843fca628556d", "item_id": "86273c707e:8", "text": "Engine Host"}
{"id": "dfa9f1c846fe24265f95fece1d8c2ba92d232c275dbf8cb35f0b18b4c5008bfe", "item_id": "86273c707e:9", "text": "The hostname of the machine running the Tractor Engine."}
{"id": "220504fec427daa0be05e52626256bf63c29486fe35b82a3a69d03a9e02e1af3", "item_id": "86273c707e:10", "text": "Engine Port"}
{"id": "11e923adcf978ee8a646c72f04790bef3d80cfd8dbadc74385cd20f9f4f50c5d", "item_id": "86273c707e:11", "text": "The port of where the Tractor Engine is listening.  The default is 80"}
{"id": "b512d97e7cbf97c273e4db073bbb547aa65a84589227f8f3d9e4a72b9372a24d", "item_id": "86273c707e:12", "text": "User"}
{"id": "e4d8956b440c6188ed831dc0f02f6b5298725a36c68430d6a244ff607bab6bb7", "item_id": "86273c707e:13", "text": "The username of who is submitting the jobs."}
{"id": "e159b06187d369a0615f66ce577582b5c983d4ea59b3a62b702049f61753f0bf", "item_id": "86273c707e:14", "text": "Paused"}
{"id": "01df9fb809f7e09ef318d48665fdaad34f33000e23853287d823c3da69c1eb51", "item_id": "86273c707e:15", "text": "Jobs will be spooled as paused when this option is selected."}
{"id": "447d9363f7225cf710a5bbc4e1a4200b14ca968bee921b086dfe00b3d13fa1a8", "item_id": "86273c707e:16", "text": "Delete Temp Files"}
{"id": "ec1b9a525ddcabd2d4d1f930d30a291a3e0da3b584e84a7a42306091e712f57a", "item_id": "86273c707e:17", "text": "Delete all temp files needed for batch rendering"}
{"id": "d60dbba079223254d4c49c230a515bc107a997e69f811365da2387f8557b9cec", "item_id": "86273c707e:18", "text": "Priority"}
{"id": "391c40df5dcf044ca929a4359041dac778d7537c280e7fd677970bd2a9367361", "item_id": "86273c707e:19", "text": "Priority of your job."}
{"id": "d677190e0a9990e7d5fa9e4c1bbde44271fb8959c4acb6d43e02ed991128b4bf", "item_id": "86273c707e:20", "text": "Service"}
{"id": "0b40b060550964456573fa9bb9dbf6d776eb35096f32b6c1db93e6fd7be22027", "item_id": "86273c707e:21", "text": "Service keys for your job."}
{"id": "0a4679ac1177b0e9bdd1cd17fdf93eb6ef15bb8ecbd7d1d63f342c74946d216d", "item_id": "86273c707e:22", "text": "Env Keys"}
{"id": "e9b0a815759213b8042fb45e115bfa2d73441ca0f59e8404ce1ca86eec66b33f", "item_id": "86273c707e:23", "text": "Multiple keys can be specified and should be space-separated."}
{"id": "4303bc09b0f601bc006f05765c5e2de767362ed13f9174dc78b82e666394c062", "item_id": "86273c707e:24", "text": "These environment keys are recognized by LocalQueue and Tractor out of box:"}
{"id": "0c36332ad8d2cfeb5964dab3a2eb5534078e6ef0e91f3685cf0b7cab0106a2fc", "item_id": "86273c707e:25", "text": "- prman-* (eg. prman-24.0)"}
{"id": "1e7e2b445c797b264509d389c92ad65b33c8f217e02b5bd1296a1253dfd5b348", "item_id": "86273c707e:26", "text": "- rmantree=* (eg. rmantree=$RMANTREE)"}
{"id": "d0d7729ba70c6b11cd75e41545e9bf71e1b47bd7fe89dfbd923dd4200008edd9", "item_id": "86273c707e:28", "text": "Delay the start of job processing until a given time"}
{"id": "544ba0516fd8e5c06858b28f1f71b0630a52f5ef2e69b9eb26ac7cfaa80dfc8b", "item_id": "86273c707e:29", "text": "Format: MONTH/DAY HOUR:MINUTES"}
{"id": "7a88fbd78bcf9a12f5fb9cda8a951ee635d0bb36055a718dc8db92582a2a1177", "item_id": "86273c707e:30", "text": "For example : 11/24 13:45"}
{"id": "c1f4e23e514e1afba0ed7746b72053757d252f5ae10bb788c476aa42ad25149a", "item_id": "86273c707e:31", "text": "Crews"}
{"id": "438571dc2bb415d8be4ef91a8712357e23a9521301a5847ad7230d337e685763", "item_id": "86273c707e:32", "text": "List of crews."}
{"id": "1eae7b58e784ce762caa0c5888578002c76009df402d9da5643d6954baa4bc4d", "item_id": "86273c707e:33", "text": "See 'Crews' in the Tractor documentation."}
{"id": "cb9e8664edea8cf5965fb4d4d013974ef10caeaad734702b19617210828cd7ab", "item_id": "86273c707e:34", "text": "Tier"}
{"id": "d899356e0a8cf86366bff2bcdff9cb245e8bd2423889a1d54826a4a38df9e512", "item_id": "86273c707e:35", "text": "Dispatching tier that the job belongs to."}
{"id": "d24abb4a3f06cc6c73ac5117314c5b7a89925c9e68dc6edc6add0b126335a195", "item_id": "86273c707e:36", "text": "See Scheduling Modes' in the Tractor documentation."}
{"id": "04e2a9728af7584043c5d58ae29e7cd811883e8dab15fc6287675270669a3ada", "item_id": "86273c707e:37", "text": "Projects"}
{"id": "69032d91e738d976c4e21a9034a362e01b3a83fb96f8ced97fc0d6f550c5b992", "item_id": "86273c707e:38", "text": "Project that job belongs to."}
{"id": "048c97c5d0c0bfd0511b3e71bcde98ee7e7a4f2911166d1d4ee7c565d42a1e79", "item_id": "86273c707e:39", "text": "See 'Limits Configuration' in the Tractor documentation"}
{"id": "355f79f29d7d3c2df917ad07f7441e3ce4b0ac48892b778076dbdca401851712", "item_id": "86273c707e:41", "text": "Comments"}
{"id": "28428af7f2767919954fa75523b1aee3ab3617b3b848a24d0ab3cb44285b1947", "item_id": "86273c707e:42", "text": "Additional comment about the job"}
{"id": "9eddf573cb509f1f62df633e25c052ac1b2a0ff9241e70223c77c73e834c0045", "item_id": "86273c707e:43", "text": "Metadata"}
{"id": "61a738c61ecbbbb2c0bca3aef70cb115c5fe16e79c2fcf5efb3e3e18c7d4f8cb", "item_id": "86273c707e:44", "text": "Meta data to add to the job."}
{"id": "50886b93ae7338bcec5e0d16a15130df9aa0592d62aee3d3c02b3e4fbbd2e8a6", "item_id": "86273c707e:45", "text": "When Done Command"}
{"id": "a2d3c93645f79b02bc84369ae2c6209b7522487019275f9c40b92cec93c7789c", "item_id": "86273c707e:46", "text": "Command to run when job completes without error."}
{"id": "b614de6909b79e4e093a52c93f0f8b8b2637b01d27cdcd879af5711cd49e078f", "item_id": "86273c707e:47", "text": "When Always Command"}
{"id": "28f9fb6e847dc004aeea3eaaa42f9cb193b6c01082d2118476d08a4f0280a154", "item_id": "86273c707e:48", "text": "Command to run regardless if job completes with or without errors."}
